data.title: Have You Seen The Matrix Resurrections Yet? Enter to Win It Now!
data.meta_description: Ready to dive back into The Matrix with the latest installment, 23 years later to own digitally? Reenter the mind-bending and thrilling world of two realities!
data.text:
Can you believe it's been 23 years since The Matrix premiered? It looks like Keanu Reeves hasn't aged a bit until you go to where it all began. Wow! Talk about a time capsule. If you loved Morpheus, get ready to have your mind blown with nostalgia and fresh views!

KEANU REEVES AND CARRIE-ANNE MOSS RETURN AS NEO AND TRINITY. REENTER THE MIND-BENDING AND THRILLING WORLD OF TWO REALITIES WITH THEM IN “THE MATRIX RESURRECTIONS.” OWN NOW, WATCH INSTANTLY!

I don't want to give you spoilers but I will say the meet-cute is exceptional! Below you can watch the trailer to see what's in store and get ready because it's just as it was but not at all. Which pill would you take?

We're giving away digital The Matrix Resurrections movies so listen on-air with Sarah J between 10 am - 3 pm weekdays for your chance to win the film and have access to it within minutes via stream! If you just can't wait, message us via the app and let us know if which pill you would take, the red or the blue? To win while supplies last!
